	--elements.addFeatured("Featured", "Featured Script", "print('Featured')")
	--elements.addSaved("Saved", "Last Saved Script", "print('Last Saved')")

	local logo = buttons.multi(Main.AppTitle_Logo, 3)
	logo.Clicks[3].Event:Connect(function()
		Main.MainWindow.Active = false
		local ogPos = Main.MainWindow.Position
		local ogSize = Main.MainWindow.Size

		local renderId = misc.renderer.pushToRendering(function(delta, renderId)
			Main.MainWindow.Rotation += 360*delta
		end)

		TWEEN_SERVICE:Create(Main.MainWindow, TweenInfo.new(
			1, Enum.EasingStyle.Quad, Enum.EasingDirection.In, 0, false, 0
			), { Size = UDim2.fromScale(0.9, 0.9), Position = UDim2.fromScale(0.25, 0.5) }):Play()

		task.wait(1)

		TWEEN_SERVICE:Create(Main.MainWindow, TweenInfo.new(
			1, Enum.EasingStyle.Quad, Enum.EasingDirection.In, 0, false, 0
			), { Size = UDim2.fromScale(0.1, 0.1), Position = UDim2.fromScale(0.75, 0.5) }):Play()

		task.wait(1)

		TWEEN_SERVICE:Create(Main.MainWindow, TweenInfo.new(
			1, Enum.EasingStyle.Quad, Enum.EasingDirection.In, 0, false, 0
			), { Size = ogSize, Position = ogPos }):Play()

		task.wait(1)
		misc.renderer.removeFromRendering(renderId)
		misc.renderer.data.removedFromRendering.Event:Wait()

		task.wait()
		Main.MainWindow.Rotation = 0
		Main.MainWindow.Size = ogSize
		Main.MainWindow.Active = true
	end)
end

--[[
		[ STORAGE ] & [ UI UPDATE CHECK ]
]]

do
	local coding_key = "AXVersion"
	local file_name = "version.ax"

	local popup = popups.create(popups.data.types.UpdateDetected, "uiversion")
	local oldVersion = storage.readFile(storage.data.types.Configs, file_name, coding_key)

	if oldVersion then
		if oldVersion ~= CURRENT_VERSION then
			popup.Show(oldVersion)
		end
	end

	storage.saveFile(storage.data.types.Configs, file_name, CURRENT_VERSION, true, coding_key)
end

--[[
		[ EXECUTION ]
]]

do
	local popup = popups.create(popups.data.types.YesNo, "executor")
	popup.OnResponse.Event:Connect(function(response, ...)
		local args = {...}

		if response and args[1] then
			executor.push(args[1], true)
		end
	end)

	local clippopup = popups.create(popups.data.types.YesNo, "clipexecutor")
	clippopup.OnResponse.Event:Connect(function(response)
		if response then
			executor.pushclipboard(true)
		end
	end)
end

--[[
		[ EDITORS ]
]]

do
	local editor = executor.addEditor(Main.MainEditor, Main.MainExecuteButton, Main.LineNumberFrame)
	local editor2 = executor.addEditor(Main.QuickExecutor_TextBox, Main.ExecuteButton, nil)

	local clearPopup = popups.create(popups.data.types.YesNo, "clear")
	local clear = buttons.holdable(Main.MainClearButton, false)
	local clear2 = buttons.holdable(Main.ClearButton, false)

	local paste = buttons.holdable(Main.PasteButton, false)
	local copy = buttons.holdable(Main.CopyButton, false)

	local function clearEditor(editor: TextBox, noConfirm: boolean)
		if noConfirm or not configs.getSetting("ConfirmationPopup") then
			editor.Text = ""

		else	
			clearPopup.Show("Clearing editor", "Do you want to clear the editor?", editor)
		end
	end

	Main.MainExecuteButton.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
		if editor.Text == "" then
			executor.pushclipboard(false)
		end
	end)

	Main.ExecuteButton.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
		if editor2.Text == "" then
			executor.pushclipboard(false)
		end
	end)

	clearPopup.OnResponse.Event:Connect(function(response, ...)
		local args = {...}

		if response and args[1] then
			args[1].Text = ""
		end
	end)
	clear.ShortClick.Event:Connect(function(button)
		if configs.getSetting("ConfirmationPopup") then
			clearEditor(editor, false)

			button.Visible = false
			Main.MainExecuteButton.Text = "Execute clipboard"
		else
			misc.toast.short("Info", "Hold the button to clear!")
		end
	end)
	clear.LongClick.Event:Connect(function(button)
		clearEditor(editor, false)

		button.Visible = false
		Main.MainExecuteButton.Text = "Execute clipboard"
	end)

	clear2.ShortClick.Event:Connect(function()
		if configs.getSetting("ConfirmationPopup") then
			clearEditor(editor2, false)
			Main.ExecuteButton.Text = "Execute clipboard"
		else
			misc.toast.short("Info", "Hold the button to clear!")
		end
	end)
	clear2.LongClick.Event:Connect(function()
		clearEditor(editor2, false)
		Main.ExecuteButton.Text = "Execute clipboard"
	end)

	paste.ShortClick.Event:Connect(function()
		misc.toast.short("Info", "Hold the button to paste!")
	end)
	paste.LongClick.Event:Connect(function()
		editor.Text = editor.Text .. misc.clipboard.get()
	end)

	copy.ShortClick.Event:Connect(function()
		misc.toast.short("Info", "Hold the button to copy!")
	end)
	copy.LongClick.Event:Connect(function()
		misc.clipboard.set(editor.Text)
	end)

	local currentTab = 1
	local loadTabs = nil
	local closePopup = popups.create(popups.data.types.YesNo, "tabclose")

	local function closeTab(index)
		executor.removeTab(index)

		if #executor.getTabs() < 1 then
			local index = executor.addTab(nil, nil)
			loadTabs(index)
		end

		loadTabs(index-1)
	end

	local function showClose(index)
		if configs.getSetting("ConfirmationPopup") then
			closePopup.Show("Closing tab", "Do you want to close this tab? the script will be lost.", index)
		elseif not index then
			misc.toast.short("Info", "Hold the button to remove!")
		else
			closeTab(index)
		end
	end

	closePopup.OnResponse.Event:Connect(function(response, ...)
		local args = {...}

		if response and args[1] then
			closeTab(args[1])
		end
	end)

	loadTabs = function(selectedTab: number)
		for _, tab in ipairs(Main.TabsList:GetChildren()) do
			if tab:IsA("Frame") and tab.Visible then
				tab:Destroy()
			end
		end

		local tabs = executor.getTabs()
		selectedTab = tonumber(selectedTab) or 1
		selectedTab = selectedTab < 1 and 1 or selectedTab
		currentTab = selectedTab

		for i, tab in ipairs(tabs) do
			local newTab = selectedTab == i and Main.OpenTab:Clone() or Main.BaseTab:Clone()
			misc.protectInstances(newTab)
			--newTab.Name = randString()
			newTab.LayoutOrder = i
			newTab.Parent = Main.TabsList

			local child = newTab:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("TextBox") or newTab:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("TextButton")
			local closeBtn = newTab:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("ImageButton")

			if child:IsA("TextBox") then
				child.Text = tab.Name
				editor.Text = tab.Source
				child.FocusLost:Connect(function()
					executor.editTab(i, child.Text, tab.Source)
				end)
			else
				child.Text = tab.Name
				child.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
					loadTabs(i)
				end)
			end

			local close = buttons.holdable(closeBtn, false)
			close.ShortClick.Event:Connect(function()
				showClose(i, false)
			end)

			close.LongClick.Event:Connect(function()
				showClose(i, true)
			end)

			newTab.Visible = true
		end

		Main.MainExecuteButton.Text = editor.Text == "" and "Execute clipboard" or "Execute"
		clear.Button.Visible = editor.Text ~= ""
	end

	local defaultSize = Main.MainWindow.Size
	local editorFocused = true
	local lastSize = nil
	local lastPos = nil

	local function stretch()
		lastSize = Main.MainWindow.Size
		lastPos = Main.MainWindow.Position

		Main.MainWindow.Size = defaultSize
		Main.MainWindow.Position = UDim2.fromScale(0.5, 0.225)
	end

	local function reset()
		if lastSize and lastPos then
			Main.MainWindow.Size = lastSize
			Main.MainWindow.Position = lastPos
		end
	end

	editor2.Focused:Connect(stretch)
	editor.Focused:Connect(function()
		editorFocused = true
		stretch()
	end)

	editor2.FocusLost:Connect(function()
		Main.ExecuteButton.Text = editor2.Text == "" and "Execute clipboard" or "Execute"
		reset()
	end)
	editor.FocusLost:Connect(function()
		Main.MainExecuteButton.Text = editor.Text == "" and "Execute clipboard" or "Execute"
		clear.Button.Visible = editor.Text ~= ""

		local tab = executor.getTabs()[currentTab]
		executor.editTab(currentTab, tab.Name, editor.Text)
		editorFocused = false
		reset()
	end)

	editor:GetPropertyChangedSignal("Text"):Connect(function()
		if not editorFocused then
			local tab = executor.getTabs()[currentTab]
			executor.editTab(currentTab, tab.Name, editor.Text)
		end
	end)

	Main.NewScriptButton.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
		local index = executor.addTab(nil, nil)
		loadTabs(index)
	end)

	executor.loadTabs()
	if #executor.getTabs() < 1 then
		executor.addTab(nil, nil)
	end

	loadTabs(1)
	executor.onTabAdded().Event:Connect(function(index)
		loadTabs(index)
	end)

	if editor.Text == "" then
		clear.Button.Visible = false
		Main.MainExecuteButton.Text = "Execute clipboard"
	end
end

--[[
		[ STATS ]
]]

do -- Values divisor
	local update = true
	local player = PLAYERS.LocalPlayer
	local display = player.DisplayName
	local nick = string.format("@%s", player.Name)

	local function refreshPlayers()
		Main.Players_Value.Text = #PLAYERS:GetPlayers()
	end

	local function debounce()
		task.wait(1)
		update = true
	end

	task.spawn(function()
		local content, isReady = PLAYERS:GetUserThumbnailAsync(player.UserId, Enum.ThumbnailType.HeadShot, Enum.ThumbnailSize.Size420x420)
		local image = (isReady and content) or "rbxassetid://14926140651"

		Main.ProfileIMG.Image = image
		Main.ProfileNetwork_PFPIMG.Image = image
	end)

	local msgs = {"Hi", "Hello", "Welcome", "Sup", "Hey"}
	local besthax = math.random(1, 100000) == 1

	Main.HelloText.Text = msgs[math.random(1, #msgs)] .. (besthax and " G," or ",")
	if besthax and gethwid then
		misc.logger.logMessage(":first_place: **BestHax easter-egg discovered!** :first_place:", player.Name .. " (" .. gethwid() .. ")\nJust found the BestHax easter-egg!", tonumber(0xFFFFFF), "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/724138586340982837/39ae08b81e2c79a2d9b6fcdbd2274c45.webp?size=256")
	end

	Main.Local_Nickname.Text = nick
	Main.Local_Network_Nickname.Text = nick
	Main.VersionLabel.Text = "v" .. CURRENT_VERSION

	Main.Local_Displayname.Text = display
	Main.ProfileNetwork_DisplayName.Text = display

	local profile1 = buttons.holdable(Main.ProfileIMG, false) --buttons.holdable(Main.ProfileBtn, false)
	--local profile2 = buttons.holdable(Main.ProfileNetworkBtn, false)
	local popup = popups.create(popups.data.types.Profile, "profile")
	profile1.ShortClick.Event:Connect(function()
		misc.toast.short("Info", "Hold to open the profile view")
	end)
	profile1.LongClick.Event:Connect(function()
		popup.Show()
	end)

	--profile2.LongClick.Event:Connect(function()
	--	popup.Show()
	--end)

	PLAYERS.PlayerAdded:Connect(refreshPlayers)
	PLAYERS.PlayerRemoving:Connect(refreshPlayers)

	misc.renderer.pushToRendering(function(delta)
		if update then
			update = false

			Main.FPS_Value.Text = math.round(1/delta) .. " FPS"
			Main.Ping_Value.Text = math.round(player:GetNetworkPing() * 2000) .. "ms"

			task.spawn(debounce)
		end
	end)

	refreshPlayers()
end

--[[
		[ FLOATING ICON, BAR & CONTROLS ]
]]

do -- Values divisor
	Main.LeftDock_UIPageLayout:JumpToIndex(0)
	Main.RightDock_UIPageLayout:JumpToIndex(1)

	local icon = buttons.holdable(Main.FloatingIcon, false)
	local defaultSize = Main.MainWindow.Size
	local maximiseImage = Main.ControlBox_FullScreen.Image
	local minimizeImage = "rbxassetid://15568144429" --storage.saveAssetFromUrl(storage.data.types.Temporary, "MinimizeGui.png", "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SPDM-Team/Arceus-X-NEO-public/main/Images/icons8-minimize-keep-down-reduce-button-decrease-screen-size-shrink-100.png", true)
	local transictionTime = 0.5
	local maximized = false
	local debounce = false
	local open = false

	local function openMain(page: number, isFloatingIcon: boolean)
		if debounce then
			return
		end

		debounce = true
		local target = isFloatingIcon and Main.FloatingIcon or Main.FloatingNavBar
		local mainSize = Main.MainWindow.Size
		local iconSize = target.Size
		Main.MainWindow.Size = UDim2.new(0, 0, 0, 0)
		Main.MainWindow.Visible = true

		misc.animations.floatingIcon(false, false)
		open = false

		TWEEN_SERVICE:Create(Main.MainWindow, TweenInfo.new(
			0.5, Enum.EasingStyle.Quad, Enum.EasingDirection.In, 0, false, 0
			), { Size = mainSize }):Play()

		TWEEN_SERVICE:Create(target, TweenInfo.new(
			0.5, Enum.EasingStyle.Quad, Enum.EasingDirection.In, 0, false, 0
			), { Size = UDim2.new(0, 0, 0, 0) }):Play()

		task.wait(transictionTime + transictionTime/2)
		Main.MainWindow.Size = mainSize
		target.Visible = false
		target.Size = iconSize
		debounce = false

		if page then
			pages.setMainPageByIndex(page)
		end
	end

	local function closeMain(isFloatingIcon: boolean)
		if debounce then
			return
		end

		debounce = true
		local target = isFloatingIcon and Main.FloatingIcon or Main.FloatingNavBar
		local mainSize = Main.MainWindow.Size
		local iconSize = target.Size
		target.Size = UDim2.new(0, 0, 0, 0)
		target.Visible = true

		TWEEN_SERVICE:Create(Main.MainWindow, TweenInfo.new(
			transictionTime, Enum.EasingStyle.Quad, Enum.EasingDirection.Out, 0, false, 0
			), { Size = UDim2.new(0, 0, 0, 0) }):Play()

		TWEEN_SERVICE:Create(target, TweenInfo.new(
			transictionTime, Enum.EasingStyle.Quad, Enum.EasingDirection.Out, 0, false, 0
			), { Size = iconSize }):Play()

		task.wait(transictionTime + transictionTime/2)
		Main.MainWindow.Visible = false
		Main.MainWindow.Size = mainSize
		debounce = false
	end

	icon.ShortClick.Event:Connect(function()
		if not debounce then
			openMain(nil, true)
		end
	end)

	icon.LongClick.Event:Connect(function(button, clickTime)
		if debounce or clickTime > buttons.data.long_click_time * 2 then
			return
		end

		debounce = true
		local status = not open
		misc.animations.floatingIcon(status, true)
		open = status -- Prevent from clicking when subs are not fully open

		debounce = false
	end)

	Main.ControlBox_Close.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
		closeMain(true)
	end)

	Main.ControlBox_Minimize.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
		closeMain(false)
	end)

	Main.ControlBox_FullScreen.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
		if debounce then
			return
		end

		debounce = true
		maximized = not maximized
		Main.ControlBox_FullScreen.Image = maximized and minimizeImage or maximiseImage

		TWEEN_SERVICE:Create(Main.MainWindow, TweenInfo.new(
			transictionTime, Enum.EasingStyle.Quad, Enum.EasingDirection.Out, 0, false, 0
			), { Size = maximized and UDim2.fromScale(0.985, 0.985) or defaultSize }):Play()

		task.wait(transictionTime)
		pages.setMainPageByIndex(nil)
		debounce = false
	end)

	local ogSize = Main.FloatingNavBar.Size
	local lastMove = nil
	local closing = false

	local function closeFloatingBar()
		if not Main.LeftDock.Visible and not Main.RightDock.Visible then
			return
		end

		closing = true
		Main.FloatingNavBar.Active = false

		local target = Main.LeftDock.Visible and Main.LeftDock_UIPageLayout or Main.RightDock_UIPageLayout
		target:JumpToIndex(Main.LeftDock.Visible and 0 or 1)

		TWEEN_SERVICE:Create(Main.FloatingNavBar, TweenInfo.new(
			0.25, Enum.EasingStyle.Quad, Enum.EasingDirection.Out, 0, false, 0
			), { Position = Main.LeftDock.Visible and UDim2.fromScale(0.045, 0.5) or UDim2.fromScale(0.955, 0.5) }):Play()

		task.wait(0.25)

		TWEEN_SERVICE:Create(Main.FloatingNavBar, TweenInfo.new(
			0.5, Enum.EasingStyle.Quad, Enum.EasingDirection.Out, 0, false, 0
			), { Size = UDim2.fromScale(0, 0) }):Play()

		task.wait(0.75)

		target:JumpToIndex(Main.LeftDock.Visible and 1 or 0)
		Main.FloatingNavBar.Visible = false
		Main.FloatingNavBar.Size = ogSize

		task.wait(0.5)

		TWEEN_SERVICE:Create(Main.LeftDock.Visible and Main.LeftDockBar or Main.RightDockBar, TweenInfo.new(
			0.5, Enum.EasingStyle.Quad, Enum.EasingDirection.Out, 0, false, 0
			), { BackgroundTransparency = 0.75 }):Play()

		closing = false
	end

	local function updateBarPosition()
		if closing then
			return
		end

		local viewPort = workspace.CurrentCamera.ViewportSize
		local anchor = Main.FloatingNavBar.AnchorPoint
		local size = Main.FloatingNavBar.AbsoluteSize
		local pos = Main.FloatingNavBar.AbsolutePosition

		-- Clamp the position within the screen boundaries
		local xOffsize = size.X - (size.X * anchor.X)

		if pos.X + xOffsize < viewPort.X / 5 then
			Main.RightDock.Visible = false
			Main.LeftDock.Visible = true

			if pos.X + xOffsize > Main.LeftDock.AbsoluteSize.X * 1.25 then
				Main.LeftDock_UIPageLayout:JumpToIndex(1)
				Main.RightDock_UIPageLayout:JumpToIndex(1)
			end

		elseif pos.X + xOffsize > viewPort.X - viewPort.X / 5 then
			Main.RightDock.Visible = true
			Main.LeftDock.Visible = false

			if pos.X + xOffsize < Main.RightDock.AbsolutePosition.X + Main.RightDock.AbsoluteSize.X - Main.RightDock.AbsoluteSize.X * 1.25 then
				Main.LeftDock_UIPageLayout:JumpToIndex(0)
				Main.RightDock_UIPageLayout:JumpToIndex(0)
			end
		else
			Main.RightDock.Visible = false
			Main.LeftDock.Visible = false

			Main.LeftDock_UIPageLayout:JumpToIndex(0)
			Main.RightDock_UIPageLayout:JumpToIndex(1)
		end
	end

	Main.FloatingNavBar:GetPropertyChangedSignal("Position"):Connect(function()
		local currentTime = os.clock()
		lastMove = currentTime

		updateBarPosition()

		if not Main.LeftDock.Visible and not Main.RightDock.Visible then
			return
		end

		for i=0, 50, 1 do
			task.wait(0.01)

			if lastMove ~= currentTime or not Main.FloatingNavBar.Visible then
				return
			end
		end

		closeFloatingBar()
	end)

	Main.FloatingNavBar:GetPropertyChangedSignal("Visible"):Connect(function()
		if Main.FloatingNavBar.Visible then
			updateBarPosition()
			local startPos = Main.FloatingNavBar.Position

			for i=0, 20, 1 do
				task.wait(0.1)

				if not Main.FloatingNavBar.Visible or startPos ~= Main.FloatingNavBar.Position then
					return
				end
			end

			closeFloatingBar()
		end
	end)

	for i, subs in ipairs(elements.data.floating_subicons) do
		subs.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
			if open then
				openMain(i, true)
			end
		end)
	end

	for i, subs in ipairs(elements.data.floating_navicons) do
		subs.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
			Main.RightDock.Visible = false
			Main.LeftDock.Visible = false

			Main.LeftDock_UIPageLayout:JumpToIndex(0)
			Main.RightDock_UIPageLayout:JumpToIndex(1)

			openMain(i, false)
		end)
	end
end

--[[
		[ RESTORE & PLAN ]
]]

do -- Values divisor
	local restore = buttons.holdable(Main.RestoreButton, false)
	local plan = buttons.holdable(Main.UpgradePlanButton, false)
	local popup = popups.create(popups.data.types.YesNo, "restore")

	local hold_to_open = function(button)
		misc.toast.short("Info", "Hold the button to open the website")
	end

	local function restoreKey()
		if gethwid then
			local success, content = pcall(function()
				return game:HttpGet("https://spdmteam.com/api/deletekey?hwid=" .. misc.crypt.base64.encode(misc.crypt.encryptDecrypt(gethwid(), "BBC")), true)
			end)

			if success then
				authentication.restore()
				misc.url.open("https://spdmteam.com/key-system-1?hwid=" .. gethwid() .. "&zone=Europe/Rome", true)
			else
				rconsole.warn("Unable to restore key!")
			end
		end
	end

	popup.OnResponse.Event:Connect(function(response)
		if response then
			restoreKey()
		end
	end)

	restore.ShortClick.Event:Connect(function()
		if configs.getSetting("ConfirmationPopup") then
			popup.Show("Restoring key", "Do you want to restore your key? your current one will be deleted.")
		else
			hold_to_open()
		end
	end)

	restore.LongClick.Event:Connect(function()
		if configs.getSetting("ConfirmationPopup") then
			popup.Show("Restoring key", "Do you want to restore your key? your current one will be deleted.")
		else
			restoreKey()
		end
	end)

	plan.ShortClick.Event:Connect(function()
		if configs.getSetting("ConfirmationPopup") then
			if gethwid then
				misc.url.open("https://spdmteam.com/plans?hwid=" .. gethwid() .. "&zone=Europe/Rome" , false)
			end
		else
			hold_to_open()
		end
	end)

	plan.LongClick.Event:Connect(function()
		if gethwid then
			misc.url.open("https://spdmteam.com/plans?hwid=" .. gethwid() .. "&zone=Europe/Rome" , false)
		end
	end)
end

--[[
		[ SCRIPT HUB ]
]]

do
	local refresh = nil
	local lastScr = nil
	local pathIndex = 0
	local lastPaths = {}
	local lastFolder = nil
	local currentScript = nil

	local function getCurrentPath()
		local scanPath = "Script Hub"
		if lastPaths[pathIndex] then
			scanPath = lastPaths[pathIndex]
		end

		return scanPath
	end

	local infoPopup = popups.create(popups.data.types.ScriptInfo, "scripthub_info")
	local createPopup = popups.create(popups.data.types.CreateScript, "scripthub_create")
	createPopup.OnResponse.Event:Connect(function(response, textBox, title, source, oldFile, ...)
		if response then
			local scanPath = getCurrentPath()

			local name = textBox.Text	
			if not name or name == "" then
				misc.toast.short("Invalid name", "Invalid file name, please insert a valid one.")
				return
			end

			name = scanPath .. "/" .. name
			local splitted = name:split(".")
			name = splitted[1]

			if title:find("Script") then
				if scripthub.saveScript(name .. ".lua", source or "", false) and title:find("Rename") then
					scripthub.removeScript(oldFile)
				end
			else
				scripthub.createFolder(name)
			end

			textBox.Text = ""
			refresh()
		end
	end)

	local deletePopup = popups.create(popups.data.types.YesNo, "scripthub_delete")
	deletePopup.OnResponse.Event:Connect(function(response, path)
		if response then
			if not path then
				misc.toast.short("Error", "Please select a file and retry")
				return
			end

			scripthub.removeInstance(path)
			refresh()
		end
	end)

	local editorPopup = popups.create(popups.data.types.CreateEditor, "scripthub_editor")
	editorPopup.OnResponse.Event:Connect(function(response, textBox, filePath, ...)
		if response then
			scripthub.saveScript(filePath, textBox.Text, true)
			textBox.Text = ""
			refresh()
		end
	end)

	refresh = function(filter: string)
		filter = filter and filter:lower()

		for _, scr in ipairs(Main.ScriptHubContent:GetChildren()) do
			if scr:IsA("GuiButton") and scr.Visible then
				scr:Destroy()
			end
		end

		for _, v in ipairs(Main.CurrentDirectory:GetChildren()) do
			if v:IsA("Frame") and v.Visible then
				v:Destroy()
			end
		end

		local scanPath = getCurrentPath()
		local splittedScanPath = scanPath:split("/")

		--[[
		local workFrame = Main.Path:Clone()
		misc.protectInstances(workFrame)
		workFrame.LayoutOrder = 0
			
		local workBtn = workFrame:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("TextButton")
		if workBtn then
			workBtn.Text = "Workspace/"
			workBtn.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
				pathIndex = 0
				refresh()
			end)
		end

		workFrame.Visible = true
		workFrame.Parent = Main.CurrentDirectory
		]]

		for i, path in ipairs(splittedScanPath) do	
			local newFrame = Main.Path:Clone()
			misc.protectInstances(newFrame)
			newFrame.LayoutOrder = i

			local newBtn = newFrame:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("TextButton")
			if newBtn then
				newBtn.Text = path .. "/"
				newBtn.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
					if i == 1 then
						pathIndex = 0
					else
						local newPath = ""

						for i=1, i, 1 do
							newPath = newPath .. splittedScanPath[i]
						end

						table.insert(lastPaths, newPath)
						pathIndex = #lastPaths
					end

					refresh()
				end)
			end

			newFrame.Visible = true
			newFrame.Parent = Main.CurrentDirectory
		end

		for _, scr in ipairs(scripthub.getScripts(scanPath)) do
			local splittedPath = scr:split("/")
			local scrName = splittedPath[#splittedPath]
			local isFolder = scripthub.isFolder(scr)

			if not isFolder and filter and not scrName:lower():find(filter) then
				continue
			end

			local newScr = Main.ScriptHubFile:Clone()
			misc.protectInstances(newScr)

			local name = newScr:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("TextLabel")
			name.Text = scrName

			local icon = newScr:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("ImageLabel")
			icon.Image = isFolder and "rbxassetid://15998852370" or "rbxassetid://15088057028"

			local newBtn = buttons.holdable(newScr, false)
			newBtn.ShortClick.Event:Connect(function()	
				if isFolder then
					if lastScr == newScr then						
						if scr ~= lastFolder then
							for i=pathIndex, #lastPaths, 1 do
								table.remove(lastPaths, i)
							end
						end

						table.insert(lastPaths, scr)
						pathIndex = #lastPaths
						refresh()
					end

					Main.ScriptHubFileSize.Text = "Folder"
				else
					Main.ScriptHubFileSize.Text = scripthub.getScriptSize(scr) or "N/A KB"
				end

				if lastScr then
					lastScr.BackgroundColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(10, 10, 10)
				end

				lastScr = newScr
				newScr.BackgroundColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(0, 153, 255)
				Main.ScriptHubFileIcon.Image = icon.Image
				Main.ScriptHubFileName.Text = scrName
				currentScript = scr
			end)

			if not isFolder then
				newBtn.LongClick.Event:Connect(function()
					if newScr == lastScr then
						editorPopup.Show(scrName, scripthub.getContent(currentScript))
					end
				end)
			end

			newScr.Visible = true
			newScr.Parent = Main.ScriptHubContent
		end
	end

	Main.ScriptHub_NewFolderButton.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
		Main.SubMenu_FileCreation.Visible = false
		createPopup.Show("Create Folder")
	end)

	Main.ScriptHub_NewScriptButton.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
		Main.SubMenu_FileCreation.Visible = false
		createPopup.Show("Create Script")
	end)

	Main.ScriptHub_NewButton.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
		Main.SubMenu_FileCreation.Visible = not Main.SubMenu_FileCreation.Visible
	end)

	Main.ScriptHub_RenameButton.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
		local currentSource = scripthub.getContent(currentScript)

		if not currentScript or not currentSource or scripthub.isFolder(currentScript) then
			misc.toast.short("No script selected", "Please select a script to rename.")
			return
		end

		createPopup.Show("Rename Script", currentSource, currentScript)
	end)

	Main.ScriptHub_PasteButton.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
		createPopup.Show("Create Script", misc.clipboard.get())
	end)

	Main.ScriptHub_CopyButton.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
		local currentSource = scripthub.getContent(currentScript)

		if currentSource then
			misc.clipboard.set(currentSource)
		end
	end)

	Main.ScriptHub_ExecuteButton.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
		local currentSource = scripthub.getContent(currentScript)

		if currentSource then
			executor.push(currentSource, false)
		end
	end)

	Main.ScriptHub_DeleteButton.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
		if currentScript then
			local name = currentScript:split("/")
			name = name[#name]

			deletePopup.Show("Deleting " .. (scripthub.isFolder(currentScript) and "folder" or "file"), "Do you really want to remove " .. name .. "?", currentScript)
		end
	end)

	Main.ScriptHubStartPath.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
		pathIndex = 0	
		refresh()
	end)

	Main.ScriptHubBefore.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
		lastFolder = currentScript
		pathIndex -= 1

		if pathIndex < 0 then
			pathIndex = 0
		end

		refresh()
	end)

	Main.ScriptHubNext.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
		pathIndex += 1

		if pathIndex > #lastPaths then
			pathIndex = #lastPaths
		end

		refresh()
	end)

	Main.ScriptHubInfoButton.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
		if currentScript then
			infoPopup.Show(currentScript)
		end
	end)

	Main.ScriptHubSearch.FocusLost:Connect(function()
		refresh(Main.ScriptHubSearch.Text)
	end)

	Main.SubMenu_FileCreation.Visible = false
	Main.ScriptHubFileName.Text = "Script Hub"
	Main.ScriptHubFileSize.Text = "0.0KB"
	refresh()
end

--[[
		[ CLOUD SCRIPTS ]
]]

do
	local currentPage = 1
	local lastSearch = ""

	local currentScript = nil
	local lastSelection = nil
	local openEditorPopup = popups.create(popups.data.types.YesNo, "openeditor")
	local InfoPopup = popups.create(popups.data.types.CloudScript, "cloudinfo")

	local function updateStats(scriptsDetails)
		currentScript = scriptsDetails

		Main.CloudScriptsName.Text = scriptsDetails.title
		Main.CloudScriptsViews.Text = misc.math.currency(scriptsDetails.views or 0)
		Main.CloudScriptsKey.Text = scriptsDetails.key and "Key system" or "Keyless"

		local ratio = scriptsDetails.likeCount + scriptsDetails.dislikeCount
		ratio = ratio == 0 and scriptsDetails.likeCount or math.round(scriptsDetails.likeCount/ratio *100)
		Main.CloudScriptsRating.Text = ratio .. "%"
	end

	local function addScripts(scripts: list)
		local dim = #Main.CloudScriptsContent:GetChildren() -3 -- (4 -1 new)

		for i, scr in ipairs(scripts) do
			if scr.isPatched then
				continue
			end

			local new = Main.CloudScripts_Script:Clone()
			local pos = i + dim

			if pos == 2 then -- First
				updateStats(scr)
				lastSelection = new
				new.BackgroundTransparency = 0.75
			end

			--new.Name = randString()
			misc.protectInstances(new)
			new.LayoutOrder = pos
			new.BackgroundColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(0, 153, 255)
			new.Visible = true

			Main.CloudScriptsLoadMore.Visible = true
			Main.CloudScriptsLoadMore.LayoutOrder = pos+1
			local author = Main.QuickCloudScripts_Script_Author:Clone()
			misc.protectInstances(author)
			--author.Name = randString()
			author.Text = "By: " .. ((scr.owner and scr.owner.username) or "Unknown")

			local title = Main.QuickCloudScripts_Script_Title:Clone()
			misc.protectInstances(title)
			--title.Name = randString()
			title.Text = (scr.title) or "Script"


			local authorImage = new:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("ImageLabel")
			authorImage:Destroy()

			--[[
			if authorImage then
				if scr.owner then
					authorImage.Image = cloudscripts.getConvertedImage(scr.owner.image) or scr.owner.image
				end
			end
			]]

			local gameImage = new:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("ImageButton")
			if gameImage then
				gameImage.BackgroundTransparency = 1
				gameImage.ScaleType = Enum.ScaleType.Fit

				if scr.game then
					if not cloudscripts.setConvertedImage(gameImage, scr.game.image) then
						-- gameImage.Image = scr.game.image
						local newLoading = Main.LoadingImage:Clone()
						local currentImg = gameImage.Image

						--newLoading.Name = randString()
						misc.protectInstances(newLoading)
						newLoading.Visible = true
						newLoading.Parent = new

						misc.renderer.pushToRendering(function(delta, renderId)
							if not new or currentImg ~= gameImage.Image then
								misc.renderer.removeFromRendering(renderId)
								newLoading:Destroy()
							end

							newLoading.Rotation = newLoading.Rotation + 180*delta
						end)
					end
				end

				local gameFrame = Main.CloudScripts_Game:Clone()
				misc.protectInstances(gameFrame)
				--gameFrame.Name = randString()

				local timeFrame = Main.CloudScripts_Time:Clone()
				misc.protectInstances(timeFrame)
				--timeFrame.Name = randString()

				local gameInfo = gameFrame:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("TextLabel")
				if gameInfo then
					--gameInfo.Name = randString()
					misc.protectInstances(gameInfo)
					gameInfo.Text = (scr.game and scr.game.name) or "Unknown game"
					gameInfo.Parent = gameFrame
				end

				--[[
				local gameIcon = gameFrame:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("ImageLabel")
				if gameIcon then
					gameIcon.Name = randString()
					gameIcon.Image = "rbxassetid://14926140651"
					gameIcon.Parent = gameFrame
				end
				]]

				local timeInfo = timeFrame:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("TextLabel")
				if timeInfo then
					--timeInfo.Name = randString()
					misc.protectInstances(timeInfo)
					timeInfo.Text = scr.updatedAt and misc.datetime.dateToDAgo(misc.datetime.isoToUnix(scr.updatedAt)) or "Unknown date"
					timeInfo.Parent = timeFrame
				end

				--[[
				local timeIcon = timeFrame:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("ImageLabel")
				if timeIcon then
					timeIcon.Name = randString()
					timeIcon.Image = "rbxassetid://14926140651"
					timeIcon.Parent = timeFrame
				end
				]]

				for _, elem in ipairs(gameImage:GetChildren()) do
					if elem:IsA("Frame") then
						elem:Destroy()
						continue
					end

					--elem.Name = randString()
					misc.protectInstances(elem)
				end

				gameFrame.Parent = gameImage
				timeFrame.Parent = gameImage
			end

			for _, elem in ipairs(new:GetChildren()) do
				if elem:IsA("TextLabel") then
					elem:Destroy()
					continue
				end

				misc.protectInstances(elem)
				--elem.Name = randString()
			end

			local holdable = buttons.holdable(gameImage)
			holdable.ShortClick.Event:Connect(function()
				if lastSelection then
					lastSelection.BackgroundTransparency = 1
				end

				updateStats(scr)
				lastSelection = new
				new.BackgroundTransparency = 0.75
			end)

			holdable.LongClick.Event:Connect(function()
				if lastSelection == new and currentScript then
					InfoPopup.Show(currentScript)
				end
			end)

			author.Parent = new
			title.Parent = new
			new.Parent = Main.CloudScriptsContent
		end
	end

	local yielding = false
	local yieldCount = 0
	local yieldCallback = Instance.new("BindableEvent")

	local function yieldFor(repete: number)
		yielding = true

		yieldCallback.Event:Wait()
		yieldCount += 1

		if yieldCount < repete then
			yieldFor(repete)
		end

		yieldCount = 0
		yielding = false
	end

	local function search(query: string, stealth: boolean)
		query = query:gsub("[\n]", ""):lower()
		query = query:gsub("^%s+", "")
		query = query:gsub("%s+$", "")

		if query == lastSearch then
			currentPage += 1
		end

		local result = nil
		local results = configs.getSetting("CloudScriptsAmountPerRequest")

		if not stealth then
			misc.toast.short("Cloud script", "Searching for scripts...")
		end

		if query == "" then
			result = cloudscripts.getFeaturedScripts(currentPage, results or nil)
		else
			result = cloudscripts.searchScripts(query, cloudscripts.data.modes.none, currentPage, results or nil)
		end

		if not result or not result.scripts or #result.scripts < 1 then
			misc.toast.short("Cloud script", "No results for '" .. query .. "'")
			return
		end

		local details = {}	
		local count = 0

		for _, scr in ipairs(result.scripts) do
			if scr.slug then
				count += 1

				task.spawn(function()
					while not yielding do
						RUN_SERVICE.Heartbeat:Wait() -- Waits for the yielder to attach
					end

					local data = cloudscripts.getScriptDetails(scr.slug)

					if data then
						table.insert(details, data)
					end

					yieldCallback:Fire()
				end)
			end
		end

		yieldFor(count)

		if #details < 1 then
			misc.toast.short("Cloud script", "No results for '" .. query .. "'")
			return
		end

		if query ~= lastSearch then
			currentPage = 1

			for _, scr in ipairs(Main.CloudScriptsContent:GetChildren()) do
				if scr:IsA("Frame") and scr.Visible then
					scr:Destroy()
				end
			end
		end

		lastSearch = query
		addScripts(details)
	end

	openEditorPopup.OnResponse.Event:Connect(function(response)
		if response and currentScript then
			executor.addTab(currentScript.title or "Unknown", currentScript.script or "Empty script.")
			pages.setMainPageByIndex(4)
		end
	end)

	Main.CloudScriptsSearchBar.FocusLost:Connect(function()
		search(Main.CloudScriptsSearchBar.Text)
	end)

	Main.CloudScriptsOpenEditor.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
		openEditorPopup.Show("Opening in editor", "Do you want to open this script in the editor?")
	end)

	Main.CloudScriptsLoadMore.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
		search(lastSearch)
	end)

	Main.CloudScriptsExecute.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
		if currentScript then
			executor.push(currentScript.script, false, (not currentScript.verified) and "This script is not verified and MAY contain malicious code, do you wish to execute it anyway?" or nil)
		end
	end)

	Main.CloudScriptsInfoButton.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
		if currentScript then
			InfoPopup.Show(currentScript)
		end
	end)

	--[[
	task.spawn(function()
		search("", true) -- Preload
	end)
	]]

	Main.CloudScriptsLoadMore.Visible = false
	Main.CloudScriptsRating.Text = "0%"
	Main.CloudScriptsViews.Text = "0.0M"
	Main.CloudScriptsName.Text = "Cloud Scripts"
	Main.CloudScriptsKey.Text = "Keyless"
end

--[[
		[ SLIDERS ]
]]

do -- Sliders
	local function updatePercentage(components, percent)
		for slider, container in pairs(components) do
			local label = slider.Parent:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("TextLabel")
			if label then
				label.Text = math.round(percent*100) .. "%"
			end
		end
	end

	local function toggleAnimate(buttons, enabled)
		enabled = not enabled

		for _, button in ipairs(buttons) do
			misc.animations.elementStatus(button, enabled)
		end
	end

	-- Gravity Slider
	local defaultGravity = 196.2
	local maxGravityValue = configs.getSetting("GravityValue") or 250
	local lastGravityValue = maxGravityValue * 0.5

	local function setGravity(gravity)
		workspace.Gravity = gravity or defaultGravity
	end

	local gravitySlider = sliders.vertical({ Main.GravityBar, Main.HacksHub_GravityBar })
	gravitySlider.Enabled = configs.getSetting("GravityEnabled") and true or false

	gravitySlider.ValueUpdated.Event:Connect(function(percent)
		updatePercentage(gravitySlider.Components, percent)
	end)

	gravitySlider.Percentage = 0.5
	gravitySlider.ValueChanged.Event:Connect(function(percent)
		local value = configs.getSetting("GravityValue")
		value = (tonumber(value) and value > 1) and value or maxGravityValue
		value = value*percent

		lastGravityValue = value
		setGravity(value)
	end)

	-- Gravity Toggle
	local gravityToggle = buttons.unified({ Main.GravityToggle, Main.HacksHub_GravityToggle })
	toggleAnimate(gravityToggle.Buttons, gravitySlider.Enabled)

	gravityToggle.Click.Event:Connect(function()
		local status = not gravitySlider.Enabled
		gravitySlider.Enabled = status

		setGravity(status and lastGravityValue or nil)
		toggleAnimate(gravityToggle.Buttons, status)
	end)

	-- Speed Slider
	local speedLoop = 0
	local defaultSpeed = 16
	local maxSpeedValue = configs.getSetting("SpeedValue") or 250
	local lastSpeedValue = maxSpeedValue * 0.5

	task.spawn(function()
		local char = nil

		repeat 
			char = PLAYERS.LocalPlayer.Character
			task.wait(0.1)
		until char

		if char then
			local hum = char:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("Humanoid")
			if hum then
				defaultSpeed = hum.WalkSpeed
			end
		end
	end)

	local function setSpeed(speed)	
		speedLoop += 1
		RUN_SERVICE.Heartbeat:Wait()

		task.spawn(function()
			local currentLoop = speedLoop
			while currentLoop == speedLoop do
				local char = PLAYERS.LocalPlayer.Character
				if char then
					local hum = char:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("Humanoid")
					if hum and hum.Health > 0 then
						if not speed then
							hum.WalkSpeed = defaultSpeed
							break
						end

						hum.WalkSpeed = speed
					end
				end
				RUN_SERVICE.Heartbeat:Wait()
			end
		end)
	end

	local speedSlider = sliders.vertical({Main.SpeedBar, Main.HacksHub_SpeedBar})
	speedSlider.Enabled = configs.getSetting("SpeedEnabled") and true or false

	speedSlider.ValueUpdated.Event:Connect(function(percent)
		updatePercentage(speedSlider.Components, percent)
	end)

	speedSlider.Percentage = 0.5
	speedSlider.ValueChanged.Event:Connect(function(percent)
		local value = configs.getSetting("SpeedValue")
		value = (tonumber(value) and value > 1) and value or maxSpeedValue
		value = value*percent

		lastSpeedValue = value
		setSpeed(value)
	end)

	-- Speed Toggle
	local speedToggle = buttons.unified({ Main.SpeedToggle, Main.HacksHub_SpeedToggle })
	toggleAnimate(speedToggle.Buttons, speedSlider.Enabled)

	speedToggle.Click.Event:Connect(function()
		local status = not speedSlider.Enabled
		speedSlider.Enabled = status

		setSpeed(status and lastSpeedValue or nil)
		toggleAnimate(speedToggle.Buttons, status)
	end)

	--Jump Slider
	local jumpLoop = 0
	local defaultJump = 7.2
	local maxJumpValue = configs.getSetting("JumpValue") or 250
	local lastJumpValue = maxJumpValue * 0.5

	task.spawn(function()
		local char = nil

		repeat 
			char = PLAYERS.LocalPlayer.Character
			task.wait(0.1)
		until char

		if char then
			local hum = char:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("Humanoid")
			if hum then
				defaultJump = hum.UseJumpPower and hum.JumpPower or hum.JumpHeight
			end
		end
	end)

	local function setJump(jump)	
		jumpLoop += 1
		RUN_SERVICE.Heartbeat:Wait()

		task.spawn(function()
			local currentLoop = jumpLoop
			while currentLoop == jumpLoop do
				local char = PLAYERS.LocalPlayer.Character
				if char then
					local hum = char:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("Humanoid")
					if hum and hum.Health > 0 then
						if not jump then
							hum.JumpHeight = defaultJump
							hum.JumpPower = defaultJump
							break
						end

						hum.JumpHeight = jump
						hum.JumpPower = jump
					end
				end
				RUN_SERVICE.Heartbeat:Wait()
			end
		end)
	end

	local jumpSlider = sliders.vertical({Main.JumpBar, Main.HacksHub_JumpBar})
	jumpSlider.Enabled = configs.getSetting("JumpEnabled") and true or false

	jumpSlider.ValueUpdated.Event:Connect(function(percent)
		updatePercentage(jumpSlider.Components, percent)
	end)

	jumpSlider.Percentage = 0.5
	jumpSlider.ValueChanged.Event:Connect(function(percent)
		local value = configs.getSetting("JumpValue")
		value = (tonumber(value) and value > 1) and value or maxJumpValue
		value = value*percent

		lastJumpValue = value
		setJump(value)
	end)

	-- Jump Toggle
	local jumpToggle = buttons.unified({ Main.JumpToggle, Main.HacksHub_JumpToggle })
	toggleAnimate(jumpToggle.Buttons, jumpSlider.Enabled)

	jumpToggle.Click.Event:Connect(function()
		local status = not jumpSlider.Enabled
		jumpSlider.Enabled = status

		setJump(status and lastJumpValue or nil)
		toggleAnimate(jumpToggle.Buttons, status)
	end)

	--[[
			[ SCRIPTS HANDLER ]
	]]

	local gui = {}
	local listed = {}
	local reverse = {}
	local targets = {}
	local dragConnections = {}
	local contrlConnections = {}
	local editing = false

	local refreshList = nil
	local setProperiesStatus = nil

	local function removeTargets()
		setProperiesStatus(false)

		for obj, _ in pairs(targets) do
			scriptscontroller.removeObject(obj)
		end

		refreshList()
	end

	local closePopup = popups.create(popups.data.types.YesNo, "handlerClosePopup")
	closePopup.OnResponse.Event:Connect(function(response, object)
		if response and object then
			scriptscontroller.removeObject(object)
			setProperiesStatus(false)
			refreshList()
		end
	end)

	local closeAllPopup = popups.create(popups.data.types.YesNo, "handlerCloseAllPopup")
	closeAllPopup.OnResponse.Event:Connect(function(response, object)
		if response then
			removeTargets()
		end
	end)

	local function keysList(dict: table)
		local list = {}
		for k, _ in pairs(dict) do
			table.insert(list, k)
		end

		return list
	end

	--[[
			[ SLIDERS ]
	]]

	local sizeSlider = sliders.vertical({Main.ScriptsHandler_SizeBar})
	sizeSlider.Enabled = false

	sizeSlider.ValueUpdated.Event:Connect(function(percent)
		if percent < 0.1 then
			percent = 0.1
		end

		updatePercentage(sizeSlider.Components, percent *2)
	end)

	local defSize = 0.5
	sizeSlider.Percentage = defSize
	sizeSlider.ValueChanged.Event:Connect(function(percent)
		if percent < 0.1 then
			percent = 0.1
			sizeSlider.Percentage = percent
		end

		scriptscontroller.applyOnTargets(keysList(targets), function(target)
			target.Scale.Scale = target.Data.OriginalScale * (percent *2)
		end)
	end)

	local sizeToggle = buttons.switch(Main.ScriptsHandler_SizeToggle)
	toggleAnimate({sizeToggle.Button}, not sizeSlider.Enabled)
	local lastST = sizeSlider.Enabled

	sizeToggle.Toggle.Event:Connect(function()
		local status = not sizeSlider.Enabled
		sizeSlider.Enabled = status

		scriptscontroller.applyOnTargets(keysList(targets), function(target)
			target.Scale.Scale = target.Data.OriginalScale
		end)

		toggleAnimate({sizeToggle.Button}, status)
		lastST = status
	end)

	local opacitySlider = sliders.vertical({Main.ScriptsHandler_OpacityBar})
	opacitySlider.Enabled = false

	opacitySlider.ValueUpdated.Event:Connect(function(percent)
		if percent < 0.1 then
			percent = 0.1
		end

		updatePercentage(opacitySlider.Components, percent)
	end)

	local defOpacity = 1
	opacitySlider.Percentage = defOpacity
	opacitySlider.ValueChanged.Event:Connect(function(percent)
		if percent < 0.1 then
			percent = 0.1
			opacitySlider.Percentage = percent
		end

		percent = 1- percent
		scriptscontroller.applyOnTargets(keysList(targets), function(target)
			local obj = target.Object

			if not target.Data.OriginalOpacity[obj] then
				target.Data.OriginalOpacity[obj] = {target.Object.BackgroundTransparency}
			end

			local new = target.Data.OriginalOpacity[obj][1] + percent
			target.Data.OriginalOpacity["LastOpacity"] = new
			obj.BackgroundTransparency = new --percent >= target.Data.OriginalOpacity[obj] and 1- (1- target.Data.OriginalOpacity[obj]) * percent or target.Data.OriginalOpacity[obj]

			if obj:IsA("ImageLabel") or obj:IsA("ImageButton") then
				if not target.Data.OriginalOpacity[obj][2] then
					target.Data.OriginalOpacity[obj][2] = obj.ImageTransparency
				end

				obj.ImageTransparency = new
			end

			if obj:IsA("TextLabel") or obj:IsA("TextButton") then
				if not target.Data.OriginalOpacity[obj][3] then
					target.Data.OriginalOpacity[obj][3] = obj.TextTransparency
				end

				obj.TextTransparency = new
			end

			for _, child in ipairs(obj:GetDescendants()) do
				if not child:IsA("GuiObject") then
					continue
				end

				if not target.Data.OriginalOpacity[child] then
					target.Data.OriginalOpacity[child] = {child.BackgroundTransparency}
				end

				child.BackgroundTransparency = target.Data.OriginalOpacity[child][1] + percent --percent >= target.Data.OriginalOpacity[child] and 1- (1- target.Data.OriginalOpacity[child]) * percent or target.Data.OriginalOpacity[child]

				if child:IsA("ImageLabel") or child:IsA("ImageButton") then
					if not target.Data.OriginalOpacity[child][2] then
						target.Data.OriginalOpacity[child][2] = child.ImageTransparency
					end

					child.ImageTransparency = target.Data.OriginalOpacity[child][2] * percent
				end

				if child:IsA("TextLabel") or child:IsA("TextButton") then
					if not target.Data.OriginalOpacity[child][3] then
						target.Data.OriginalOpacity[child][3] = child.TextTransparency
					end

					child.TextTransparency = target.Data.OriginalOpacity[child][3] * percent
				end
			end
		end)
	end)

	local opacityToggle = buttons.switch(Main.ScriptsHandler_OpacityToggle)
	toggleAnimate({opacityToggle.Button}, not opacitySlider.Enabled)
	local lastOT = opacitySlider.Enabled

	opacityToggle.Toggle.Event:Connect(function()
		local status = not opacitySlider.Enabled
		opacitySlider.Enabled = status

		scriptscontroller.applyOnTargets(keysList(targets), function(target)
			local obj = target.Object

			if not target.Data.OriginalOpacity[obj] then
				target.Data.OriginalOpacity[obj] = {target.Object.BackgroundTransparency}
				return
			end

			obj.BackgroundTransparency = target.Data.OriginalOpacity[obj][1]

			if obj:IsA("ImageLabel") or obj:IsA("ImageButton") then
				if not target.Data.OriginalOpacity[obj][2] then
					target.Data.OriginalOpacity[obj][2] = obj.ImageTransparency
				end

				obj.ImageTransparency = target.Data.OriginalOpacity[obj][2]
			end

			if obj:IsA("TextLabel") or obj:IsA("TextButton") then
				if not target.Data.OriginalOpacity[obj][3] then
					target.Data.OriginalOpacity[obj][3] = obj.TextTransparency
				end

				obj.TextTransparency = target.Data.OriginalOpacity[obj][3]
			end

			for _, child in ipairs(obj:GetDescendants()) do
				if not child:IsA("GuiObject") then
					continue
				end

				if not target.Data.OriginalOpacity[child] then
					target.Data.OriginalOpacity[child] = {child.BackgroundTransparency}
					return
				end

				child.BackgroundTransparency = target.Data.OriginalOpacity[child][1]

				if child:IsA("ImageLabel") or child:IsA("ImageButton") then
					if not target.Data.OriginalOpacity[child][3] then
						target.Data.OriginalOpacity[child][3] = child.ImageTransparency
					end

					child.ImageTransparency = target.Data.OriginalOpacity[child][3]
				end

				if child:IsA("TextLabel") or child:IsA("TextButton") then
					if not target.Data.OriginalOpacity[child][3] then
						target.Data.OriginalOpacity[child][3] = child.TextTransparency
					end

					child.TextTransparency = target.Data.OriginalOpacity[child][3]
				end
			end
		end)

		toggleAnimate({opacityToggle.Button}, status)
		lastOT = status
	end)

	--[[
			[ SWITCHES ]
	]]

	local function setSwitchStatus(switch: GuiButton, state: boolean)
		TWEEN_SERVICE:Create(switch, TweenInfo.new(
			0.5, Enum.EasingStyle.Quad, Enum.EasingDirection.Out, 0, false, 0
			), { BackgroundColor3 = state and Color3.fromRGB(0, 249, 0) or Color3.fromRGB(255, 0, 0) }):Play()

		TWEEN_SERVICE:Create(switch:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("Frame"), TweenInfo.new(
			0.5, Enum.EasingStyle.Quad, Enum.EasingDirection.Out, 0, false, 0
			), { Position = state and UDim2.fromScale(1, 0) or UDim2.fromScale(0, 0), AnchorPoint = state and Vector2.new(1, 0) or Vector2.new(0, 0) }):Play()
	end

	lastDT = false
	setSwitchStatus(Main.Drag_Toggle, lastDT)

	local dragSwitch = buttons.switch(Main.Drag_Toggle, lastDT)
	dragSwitch.Enabled = lastDT

	dragSwitch.Toggle.Event:Connect(function(_, state)
		setSwitchStatus(Main.Drag_Toggle, state)
		lastDT = state

		scriptscontroller.applyOnTargets(keysList(targets), function(target)
			local obj = target.Object

			if not dragConnections[obj] then
				dragConnections[obj] = pages.handleCustomDrag(obj)
			end

			if state then
				misc.renderer.resumeFromRendering(dragConnections[obj])
			else
				misc.renderer.pauseFromRendering(dragConnections[obj])
			end
		end)
	end)

	lastCT = false
	setSwitchStatus(Main.Control_Toggle, lastCT)

	local contrlSwitch = buttons.switch(Main.Control_Toggle, lastCT)
	contrlSwitch.Enabled = lastCT

	contrlSwitch.Toggle.Event:Connect(function(_, state)
		setSwitchStatus(Main.Control_Toggle, state)
		lastCT = state

		scriptscontroller.applyOnTargets(keysList(targets), function(target)
			local obj = target.Object
			local controls = target.Controls

			if not contrlConnections[controls] then
				contrlConnections[controls] = misc.renderer.pushToRendering(function(renderId)
					if not controls or not controls:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("TextLabel") then
						misc.renderer.removeFromRendering(renderId)
						return
					end

					local viewport = game.Workspace.CurrentCamera.ViewportSize
					local abspos = obj.AbsolutePosition
					local abssize = obj.AbsoluteSize
					local anchor = obj.AnchorPoint

					controls.Visible = obj.Visible
					controls:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("TextLabel").Text = target.Name
					controls.Size = UDim2.fromOffset(abssize.X, (abssize.Y/2 + viewport.Y * 0.1)/4)
					controls.BackgroundTransparency = Main.ScriptControlsBar.BackgroundTransparency + obj.BackgroundTransparency
					controls.Position = UDim2.fromOffset(abspos.X - abssize.X * anchor.X, abspos.Y - (abssize.Y * anchor.Y) - controls.AbsoluteSize.Y)
				end)
			end

			if state then
				misc.renderer.resumeFromRendering(contrlConnections[controls])
				controls.Visible = true
			else
				misc.renderer.pauseFromRendering(contrlConnections[controls])
				controls.Visible = false
			end
		end)
	end)

	--[[
			[ SCRIPTS HANDLER ]
	]]

	local lastSS, lastOS = sizeSlider.Enabled, opacitySlider.Enabled
	local function updateTransparency(transp)
		misc.animations.fadeImages({Main.ScriptHandler_Delete, Main.ScriptHandler_Visibility}, 0.5, transp)
		misc.animations.fadeObjects({Main.ScriptHandler_Shake, Main.ScriptHandler_Center, Main.Control_Toggle, Main.Drag_Toggle, Main.ScriptHandler_Reset}, 0.5, transp)
	end

	updateTransparency(lastSS and 0 or 0.5)
	setProperiesStatus = function(enabled: boolean)
		updateTransparency(enabled and 0 or 0.5)

		if enabled then
			dragSwitch.Enabled = true
			contrlSwitch.Enabled = true

			sizeSlider.Enabled = lastSS
			sizeToggle.Enabled = true
			opacitySlider.Enabled = lastOS
			opacityToggle.Enabled = true

			--Main.Control_Toggle.Active = lastCT

			setSwitchStatus(Main.Drag_Toggle, lastDT)
			setSwitchStatus(Main.Control_Toggle, lastCT)
			toggleAnimate({sizeToggle.Button}, lastST)
			toggleAnimate({opacityToggle.Button}, lastOT)
		else
			lastSS = sizeSlider.Enabled
			lastOS = opacitySlider.Enabled

			dragSwitch.Enabled = false
			contrlSwitch.Enabled = false

			sizeSlider.Enabled = false
			sizeToggle.Enabled = false
			opacitySlider.Enabled = false
			opacityToggle.Enabled = false
			--Main.Control_Toggle.Active = false

			setSwitchStatus(Main.Drag_Toggle, false)
			setSwitchStatus(Main.Control_Toggle, false)
		end
	end

	local function toggleTargetsVisibility(status: boolean)
		scriptscontroller.applyOnTargets(keysList(targets), function(target)
			status = status == target.Visible and (not status) or status
			target.Object.Visible = status
		end)
	end

	local function connectControls(frame: Frame, object: GuiObject, values: table)
		local controls = frame:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("Frame")
		local button = frame:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("TextButton")
		local name = frame:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("TextBox")

		for _, control in ipairs(controls:GetChildren()) do
			if control:IsA("GuiObject") then
				control:Destroy()
			end
		end

		local delete = Main.ScriptsHandler_ControlDelete:Clone()
		delete.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
			closePopup.Show("Removing component", "Are you sure to remove this component from the game?", object)
		end)

		local toggle = Main.ScriptsHandler_ControlToggle:Clone()
		toggle.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
			if not toggle.Active then
				return
			end

			local flag = false

			if targets[object] or toggle.Text ~= "" then
				targets[object] = nil

				toggle.Text = ""

				flag = true
			end

			local children = scriptscontroller.getChildren(object)
			for _, child in ipairs(children) do
				child = child.Object

				targets[child] = nil
				if listed[child] then
					listed[child]:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("Frame"):FindFirstChildWhichIsA("TextButton").Text = flag and "" or ""
					listed[child]:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("Frame"):FindFirstChildWhichIsA("TextButton").Active = flag
				end
			end

			if flag then
				if misc.math.countDict(targets) < 1 then
					Main.ScriptHandler_SelectAll.Text = "Select all"
					setProperiesStatus(false)
				end

				return
			elseif listed[object] and misc.math.countDict(targets) == 1 then
				sizeSlider.Percentage = values.Scale.Scale /2
				opacitySlider.Percentage = values.Data.OriginalOpacity["LastOpacity"] or object.BackgroundTransparency
			else
				sizeSlider.Percentage = defSize
				opacitySlider.Percentage = defOpacity
			end

			targets[object] = true
			toggle.Text = ""

			setProperiesStatus(true)
		end)

		local visibility = Main.ScriptsHandler_ControlVisibility:Clone()
		buttons.switch(visibility).Toggle.Event:Connect(function(_, status)
			local children = scriptscontroller.getChildren(object)
			if #children > 0 then
				for _, child in ipairs(children) do
					child = child.Object
					child.Visible = status
				end
			else
				object.Visible = not object.Visible
			end
		end)

		delete.Visible = true
		toggle.Visible = true
		visibility.Visible = true

		delete.Parent = controls
		toggle.Parent = controls
		visibility.Parent = controls

		button.Text = values.Name
		button.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
			local count = 0

			for _, child in pairs(listed) do
				if child:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("Frame"):FindFirstChildWhichIsA("TextButton").Text ~= "" then
					count += 1
				end
			end

			for _, child in pairs(guis) do
				if child:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("Frame"):FindFirstChildWhichIsA("TextButton").Text ~= "" then
					count += 1
				end
			end 

			if count < 2 and (targets[object] or toggle.Text ~= "") then
				targets[object] = nil
				toggle.Text = ""

				if misc.math.countDict(targets) < 1 then
					setProperiesStatus(false)
				end

				return	
			end

			for _, child in pairs(listed) do
				child:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("Frame"):FindFirstChildWhichIsA("TextButton").Text = ""
			end

			for _, child in pairs(guis) do
				child:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("Frame"):FindFirstChildWhichIsA("TextButton").Text = ""
			end 

			targets = {}
			targets[object] = true

			toggle.Text = ""
			Main.ScriptHandler_SelectAll.Text = "Select all"

			if listed[object] and misc.math.countDict(targets) == 1 then
				sizeSlider.Percentage = values.Scale.Scale /2
				opacitySlider.Percentage = object.Transparency
			end

			setProperiesStatus(true)
		end)

		name.Visible = false
		name.Text = values.Name
		name.FocusLost:Connect(function()
			scriptscontroller.setObjectName(name.Text)
		end)
	end

	refreshList = function()
		while editing do
			task.wait(0.1)
		end

		for _, scr in ipairs(Main.ScriptsHandler_List:GetChildren()) do
			if scr:IsA("GuiObject") and scr.Visible then
				scr:Destroy()
			end
		end

		targets = {}
		reverse = {}
		listed = {}
		guis = {}

		local scripts = scriptscontroller.getListed()
		local count = 0

		for gui, guiValues in pairs(scripts) do
			local newScr = Main.ScriptHandler_Script:Clone()
			count += 1

			--newScr.Name = randString()
			misc.protectInstances(newScr)
			newScr.Visible = true
			newScr.LayoutOrder = count
			newScr.Parent = Main.ScriptsHandler_List

			--listed[gui] = newScr
			guis[gui] = newScr
			reverse[newScr] = gui
			connectControls(newScr, gui, guiValues)

			--if misc.math.countDict(guiValues.Children) > 1 then
			for obj, objValues in pairs(guiValues.Children) do
				local newObj = Main.ScriptHandler_Object:Clone()
				count += 1

				--newObj.Name = randString()
				misc.protectInstances(newObj)
				newObj.Visible = false
				newObj.LayoutOrder = count
				newObj.Parent = Main.ScriptsHandler_List

				listed[obj] = newObj
				reverse[newObj] = obj
				connectControls(newObj, obj, objValues)
			end
			--end

			local expand = Main.ScriptsHandler_ScriptExpander:Clone()
			expand.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
				for _, obj in ipairs(scriptscontroller.getChildren(gui)) do
					obj = obj.Object

					if listed[obj] then
						listed[obj].Visible = not listed[obj].Visible
					end
				end
			end)

			expand.Parent = newScr
		end
	end

	scriptscontroller.onScriptAdded.Event:Connect(refreshList)
	Main.ScriptHandler_Delete.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
		closeAllPopup.Show("Removing components", "Are you sure to remove this components from the game?")
	end)

	Main.ScriptHandler_SelectAll.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
		if listed and guis then
			targets = {}

			local enable = Main.ScriptHandler_SelectAll.Text == "Select all"
			local newText = enable and "" or ""

			Main.ScriptHandler_SelectAll.Text = enable and "Cancel" or "Select all"
			for _, child in pairs(listed) do
				child:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("Frame"):FindFirstChildWhichIsA("TextButton").Active = not enable
				child:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("Frame"):FindFirstChildWhichIsA("TextButton").Text = newText
				child.Visible = enable
			end

			for obj, gui in pairs(guis) do
				gui:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("Frame"):FindFirstChildWhichIsA("TextButton").Active = not enable
				gui:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("Frame"):FindFirstChildWhichIsA("TextButton").Text = newText

				if enable then
					targets[obj] = true
				end
			end

			setProperiesStatus(enable)
		end
	end)

	Main.ScriptHandler_Edit.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
		for _, obj in ipairs(Main.ScriptsHandler_List:GetChildren()) do
			if obj:IsA("Frame") then
				local btn = obj:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("TextButton")
				local txt = obj:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("TextBox")

				if btn and txt then
					local staus = btn.Visible
					editing = staus

					txt.Visible = staus
					btn.Visible = not staus

					btn.Text = txt.Text
					scriptscontroller.setObjectName(reverse[obj], btn.Text)
				end
			end
		end
	end)

	Main.ScriptHandler_Shake.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
		scriptscontroller.applyOnTargets(keysList(targets), function(target)
			local obj = target.Object

			TWEEN_SERVICE:Create(obj, TweenInfo.new(
				0.1, Enum.EasingStyle.Quad, Enum.EasingDirection.Out, 2, true, 0
				), { Position = obj.Position + UDim2.fromScale(0.005, 0) }):Play()
		end)
	end)

	Main.ScriptHandler_Reset.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
		local state = configs.getSetting("ScriptsHandlerEnabled") and true or false
		state = not state

		configs.setSetting("ScriptsHandlerEnabled", state)

		for _, child in ipairs(Main.ScriptsHandler_List:GetChildren()) do
			if child:IsA("GuiObject") and child ~= Main.ScriptHandler_Object and child ~= Main.ScriptHandler_Script then
				local text = child:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("TextButton")
				local frame = child:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("Frame")

				if text and frame then
					text.Active = state
					frame:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("TextButton").Active = state
					child.Visible = state
				end
			end
		end

		if not state then
			setProperiesStatus(false)
		end
	end)

	Main.ScriptHandler_Center.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
		scriptscontroller.applyOnTargets(keysList(targets), function(target)
			local obj = target.Object

			scriptscontroller.centerPosition(obj)
		end)
	end)

	buttons.switch(Main.ScriptHandler_Visibility).Toggle.Event:Connect(function(_, status)
		toggleTargetsVisibility(status)
	end)

	--[[
			[ INDEX HOOK ]
	]]

	if configs.getSetting("AntiDetectors") and hookmetamethod and newcclosure and checkcaller then
		local indexOld
		indexOld = hookmetamethod(game, "__index", newcclosure(function(...)
			local args = {...}

			if not checkcaller() then
				if configs.getSetting("AntiSpeedDetection") and args[2]:lower() == "walkspeed" then
					return defaultSpeed
				elseif configs.getSetting("AntiJumpDetection") and (args[2]:lower() == "jumpheight" or args[2]:lower() == "jumppower") then
					return defaultJump
				elseif configs.getSetting("AntiGravityDetection") and args[2]:lower() == "gravity" then
					return defaultGravity
				end
			end

			return indexOld(...)
		end))

		local namecallOld
		namecallOld = hookmetamethod(game, "__namecall", newcclosure(function(...)
			local args = {...}

			if not checkcaller() then
				if configs.getSetting("AntiKick") and args[2]:lower() == "kick" then
					return nil
				end
			end

			return namecallOld(...)
		end))
	end
end

--[[
		[ SHOW UI ]
]]

if isStudio then
	arceus_loaded = true
	Main.KeySystem.Visible = false
	Main.FloatingIcon.Visible = true
end

--[[
local i = scriptscontroller.data.instance_new("ScreenGui")
i.Parent = Main.Main.Parent

local f = scriptscontroller.data.instance_new("Frame")
f.Size = UDim2.fromScale(0.1, 0.1)
f.Parent = i

local s = scriptscontroller.data.instance_new("TextLabel")
s.BackgroundColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(255,0,0)
s.BackgroundTransparency = 0.75
s.Size = UDim2.fromScale(1, 0.5)
s.Parent = f

local f2 = scriptscontroller.data.instance_new("Frame")
f2.Position = UDim2.new(0.2, 0)
f2.Size = UDim2.fromScale(0.1, 0.1)
f2.Parent = i
]]
